snippet.title: Vendir: Plague of Lies Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Vendir: Plague of Lies - OUT NOW
Classic party-based RPG with an epic dark story and turn-based combat. 

Available now on Android & iOS
Play Google Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.earlymorningstudio.vendirplagueoflies
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vendir-plague-of-lies/id1542939957?platform=iphone
